name: Capital O Hotel Millennium Grand
description: Offering comfort and great services at budget rates, Capital O 23502 Hotel Millennium Grand in Hyderabad is an ideal lodging for travelers touring the city. Maintained by a skilled and friendly staff, the OYO ensures you have a good stay. The property offers TV, Free WiFi and a lot more. Safety measures are taken and facilities like fire safety, first aid and round the clock security are provided for the safety of guests. Additionally, we have a 24-hour helpdesk to offer guests assistance at any hour. Explore Hyderabad and visit the famous landmarks and attractions such as Mix Bar, Golconda Fort and Jamia Masjid among others.
